*
* PROCEDURE F:
*
* EITHER ARG1 OR ARG2 IS A NAN
*
*
* PROCEDURE NANCMP
*
*   NANCMP HANDLES A CMP WHERE EITHER ARG1 AND
* ARG2 IS A NAN.
*
NANCMP LDB  #BIT0   SET UNORDERED
*
* PROCEED TO STEP II TO EITHER SET CC REG. OR
* AFFIRM/DISAFFIRM A PREDICATE.
*
 BSR  CMPST2
*
*
 RTS   RETURN
*
*
*
 PAG
