* PROCEDURE  G:
*
* BOTH ARG1 AND ARG2 ARE ZERO
*
*
* PROCEDURE CMPZER
*
*    CMPZER HANDLES THE CASE OF COMPARE WHERE
* BOTH ARG1 AND ARG2 ARE ZERO.
*
CMPZER LDB  #BIT2  SET =
*
* PROCEED TO STEP II TO EITHER SET CC REG.
* SO AFFIRM/DISAFFIRM A PREDICATE.
*
 BSR  CMPST2
*
 RTS	RETURN
