*
*  ARG2 UNORMALIZED & ARG1 NORMALIZED
*
* PROCCEDURE  ARG2UN
*
*    ARGIUN HANDLES THE CASE OF COMPARE WHERE ARG1 IS
* UNORMALIZED. ARG1 IS NORMALIZED AS FAR AS THE LOWER BOUND ON THE
